    "slug": "watashi-nouryoku-wa-heikinchi-de-tte-itta-yo-ne",
    "titulo": "Didn't I Say To Make My Abilities Average In The Next Life?!",
    "titulo_original": "私、能力は平均値でって言ったよね!",
    "imagen": "https://myanimelist.net/images/anime/1205/111403.jpg",
